{"tid":2202853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新巴車長今提堂 職工盟籲全城聲援","createTime":"2020-09-15T02:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T04:14:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58d627b4976f31c27b5e695552c42876b4f56b06","tid":2202853,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/FOBNHXHHFBCQFBTZRALBVNZGWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FFOBNHXHHFBCQFBTZRALBVNZGWI%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=5b06c1ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FFOBNHXHHFBCQFBTZRALBVNZGWI%2F&h=fdac114a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/FOBNHXHHFBCQFBTZRALBVNZGWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新巴車長今提堂 職工盟籲全城聲援<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vG2QEP1mPcgmnrpnHFUkeS7CYc4=/1330x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AD727XFHTRHDHOH3MFXZAU65LM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvG2QEP1mPcgmnrpnHFUkeS7CYc4%3D%2F1330x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAD727XFHTRHDHOH3MFXZAU65LM.jpg&h=a8bf123e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新巴司機被濫捕引起公憤。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方本月6日在油麻地拘捕一名36歲新巴男車長，並三度改控其罪名，引起公憤，最終落案起訴他「不小心駕駛」，案件今日於九龍城裁判法院提堂。職工盟facebook發起一人一相撐車長行動，呼籲市民可以將用戶頭像換成「全城撐車長」相框，以行動聲援車長。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟在帖文中指，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將用戶頭像轉成「撐車長」<br />\n<br />\n職工盟強調，新巴司機被濫捕濫告，屬「是非黑白之分，而非罪名輕重之分」，呼籲市民參與一人一相撐車長行動，將用戶頭像換成「全城撐車長」相框，再將相片傳送至他們facebook 或Telegram：@HKCTU，以示支持新巴車長，以行動反映政府的荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NoCW7MC4RPtuQeYnQtXD_ie4Umo=/899x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S66AASEAINBVHOK7E7A2P2APLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNoCW7MC4RPtuQeYnQtXD_ie4Umo%3D%2F899x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS66AASEAINBVHOK7E7A2P2APLA.jpg&h=e931efed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■職工盟發起一人一相撐車長。"},{"pid":"5f11c340d116a675bd871cf93c20c08f8fb6d7db","tid":2202853,"uid":276191,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"撐乜鬼, 連工業行動都唔敢"},{"pid":"927784b0833dee42f38f3bdafd4e0e3a554f38a9","tid":2202853,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:39:05.000Z","msg":"出幾架巴士係法院外夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01efa029d87a5c243a23b1a829c7d3b476ffd55a","tid":2202853,"uid":26224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f11c340d116a675bd871cf93c20c08f8fb6d7db","tid":2202853,"uid":276191,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"撐乜鬼, 連工業行動都唔敢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"識巴士佬, 佢地話唔會出聲, <br />\n份工緊要. 重話人係自私好正常."},{"pid":"19b3974f3c17160be1810ceb010ee8000dacc787","tid":2202853,"uid":258706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01efa029d87a5c243a23b1a829c7d3b476ffd55a","tid":2202853,"uid":26224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f11c340d116a675bd871cf93c20c08f8fb6d7db","tid":2202853,"uid":276191,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"撐乜鬼, 連工業行動都唔敢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"識巴士佬, 佢地話唔會出聲, <br />\n份工緊要. 重話人係自私好正常."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"同普遍唔肯三罷嘅香港人一樣"},{"pid":"4527fb010920f217d8754951deed5c718446a600","tid":2202853,"uid":70238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01efa029d87a5c243a23b1a829c7d3b476ffd55a","tid":2202853,"uid":26224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f11c340d116a675bd871c